Pre-Game Insights: Estonia are aiming to get off to a strong start in this season's UEFA Nations League, when they face Slovakia at the A. Le Coq Stadium in Tallinn on Thursday evening (September 5)
Miscellaneous Highlights: Estonia will definitely be without Rasmus Peetson on Thursday, after the FCI Levadia Tallinn midfielder pulled out of the Slovakia match due to illness
Others: The match will be shown live on ETV2 and ETV+
